### Buggy Function
```java
public XmlDeclaration asXmlDeclaration() {
    String data = getData();
    Document doc = Jsoup.parse("<" + data.substring(1, data.length() - 1) + ">", baseUri(), Parser.xmlParser());
    XmlDeclaration decl = null;
